Southwestern Turkey Burger

25 min
$12.99
450 kcal
Difficulty: 30%
Servings: 4

Description

A flavorful and juicy turkey burger with a southwestern twist, perfect for a quick and satisfying meal.

Ingredients

  • ground turkey: 1 lb
  • black beans: 1/2 cup
  • corn kernels: 1/2 cup
  • chopped red onion: 1/4 cup
  • chopped cilantro: 2 tbsp
  • cheddar cheese: 1/2 cup
  • burger buns: 4
  • avocado: 1
  • lettuce leaves: 4
  • tomato slices: 4
